request.description:
### Request Description

This endpoint is used to initiate the process of resetting a forgotten password. The request should be sent as an HTTP POST to the specified URL with the email of the user who needs to reset their password provided in the request body.

#### Request Body

- email (string, required): The email address of the user who needs to reset their password.


### Response

The response for this request is in JSON format and includes the following fields:

- status (string): Indicates the status of the request, such as success or failure.

- message (string): Provides additional information or error messages related to the request.


### JSON Schema

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "status": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "message": {
      "type": "string"
    }
  }
}

 ```

